name: THE TICKLE - Issue #21
description:
Art zine focused on Hic et Nunc artists and writers.
Issue #21 is the biggest issue yet, with 31 pages featuring the works of Colin Thomas Frangicetto, Sky Goodman and Cryptofangs. This weeks literary contribution is a short story by Joanne Rush.

Created by artists Wily Guys (@guyswily) and Theo Horsmeier (@THorsmeier)
